OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy and grey start with
OL,6,Fsome showery outbreaks of rain. Skies
OL,7,Fwill brighten during the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith some hazy sunshine possibly
OL,9,Fdeveloping later. Near normal
OL,10,Ftemperatures.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy overnight,
OL,13,Fbut with a few breaks in the cloud
OL,14,Fhere and there. Some showery outbreaks
OL,15,For rain and drizzle are possible over
OL,16,Fwestern counties.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
