OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for many with
OL,6,Fpatchy drizzle, mostly in the west.
OL,7,FHowever the cloud will lift and break
OL,8,Fup readily with sunny spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping. A strengthening
OL,10,Fsouthwesterly wind later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,13,FIncreasingly changeable from
OL,14,FWednesday, with showers or longer
OL,15,Fspells of rain. Some sunny spells are
OL,16,Falso likely, with temperatures near
OL,17,Fnormal, but turning colder by Friday.
OL,18,FWindy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
